canonical:
  title: 正郞
  author: 李存吾
  language: lzh
  text: 遊學三年雪滿巖醇醪不覺自沉酣別來歲月奔如電惆悵無人爲指南
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 正郞
  author: 李存吾
  language: lzh
  text: 遊學三年雪滿巖。醇醪不覺自沉酣。別來歲月奔如電。惆悵無人爲指南。
korean:
  title: 정랑
  author: 이존오
  language: kor
  text: |-
    설만암에 유학한 지 삼 년이라 가득한데
    진국 술에 절고 취하는 줄 깨닫지 못하였다
    이별한 뒤로 세월은 번개처럼 달리는데
    나를 지도해 줄 이 아무도 없음을 슬퍼하나니
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0650&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: The Vice Director
  author: Lee Joon-oh
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Three years of study in snow-blanketed cliffs,
    In fragrant wine I drowsed, unaware of my own intoxication.
    Since parting, the months have fled like lightning—
    No one remains to guide me through this sorrow.
  footnotes:
    - The title '정랑' (Vice Director) likely refers to an official position the author held or aspired to, placing this poem in the context of a scholar-official's reflections on youth and loss.
